    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            storeUserTimezone();

            // Initialize Flatpickr for date inputs with Monday as first day
            if (typeof flatpickr !== 'undefined') {
                flatpickr('.datepicker', {
                    dateFormat: 'd/m/Y',
                    locale: {
                        firstDayOfWeek: 1 // Monday
                    }
                });
            }

            // Synchronize hover effect between fixed and scrollable columns
            const fixedTable = document.querySelector('.fixed-columns .schedule-grid tbody');
            const scrollableTable = document.querySelector('.scrollable-columns .schedule-grid tbody');

            if (fixedTable && scrollableTable) {
                const fixedRows = fixedTable.querySelectorAll('tr');
                const scrollableRows = scrollableTable.querySelectorAll('tr');

                // Add hover listeners to fixed columns
                fixedRows.forEach((row, index) => {
                    row.addEventListener('mouseenter', function() {
                        if (scrollableRows[index]) {
                            scrollableRows[index].classList.add('row-hover');
                        }
                    });

                    row.addEventListener('mouseleave', function() {
                        if (scrollableRows[index]) {
                            scrollableRows[index].classList.remove('row-hover');
                        }
                    });
                });

                // Add hover listeners to scrollable columns
                scrollableRows.forEach((row, index) => {
                    row.addEventListener('mouseenter', function() {
                        if (fixedRows[index]) {
                            fixedRows[index].classList.add('row-hover');
                        }
                    });

                    row.addEventListener('mouseleave', function() {
                        if (fixedRows[index]) {
                            fixedRows[index].classList.remove('row-hover');
                        }
                    });
                });
            }
        });

        // Skeleton loader script: Hide skeleton and show actual content when page loads
        window.addEventListener('load', function() {
            // Hide skeleton loader
            var skeletonLoader = document.getElementById('skeletonLoader');
            if (skeletonLoader) {
                skeletonLoader.style.display = 'none';
            }

            // Show actual content
            var mainContent = document.getElementById('MainContent_MainContentPanel');
            if (mainContent) {
                mainContent.style.display = 'block';
            }
        });
    </script>

        </div>
    </form>

    <script>
        // Manual link blinking effect
        (function() {
            const manualLink = document.getElementById('manualLink');
            if (!manualLink) return;

            let isUpdatedText = false;
            let blinkCount = 0;
            const maxBlinks = 5; // 10 seconds with 0.5s interval = 60 blinks

            // Don't start blinking if maxBlinks is 0
            if (maxBlinks === 0) return;

            // Add CSS transition for smooth fade
            manualLink.style.transition = 'opacity 0.3s ease-in-out';

            const blinkInterval = setInterval(function() {
                // Fade out
                manualLink.style.opacity = '0';

                setTimeout(function() {
                    // Change text
                    if (isUpdatedText) {
                        manualLink.textContent = 'Manual';
                        isUpdatedText = false;
                    } else {
                        manualLink.textContent = 'updated';
                        isUpdatedText = true;
                    }

                    // Fade in
                    manualLink.style.opacity = '1';
                }, 150); // Half of transition time

                blinkCount++;

                // Stop after 30 seconds
                if (blinkCount >= maxBlinks) {
                    clearInterval(blinkInterval);
                    // Ensure it ends on "Manual"
                    setTimeout(function() {
                        manualLink.style.opacity = '0';
                        setTimeout(function() {
                            manualLink.textContent = 'Manual';
                            manualLink.style.opacity = '1';
                        }, 150);
                    }, 500);
                }
            }, 1000); // 1 second interval
        })();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
